rComments: He is so understanding and knowledgeable about communication. He is my favorite professor yet!
If you're looking for easy A, I don't recommend this class.

Bryan is the best. He is so understanding and friendly. You can come to him with a problem and he will work through it with you. I always found myself really engaged in his lectures. He is so hilarious and energetic. He gives really constructive feedback and you can tell that he's really into the class. Wish I could take this class again.
